# chess - Connor Tynan (ctynan)

## About

Fully functional 2 player chess, with ncurses UI.

## Controls
 - Move around with `WASD`, arrow keys, or vim controls (`HJKL`)
 - Select with `Enter` or `Space`
 - Deselect with `Delete`, `Backspace` (or select an invalid square)
 - `Shift+F` to flip board
 - `Shift+Q`

## Todo
 - Undo/Redo moves in UI
